The presidential candidate of the All Progressives Congress (APC) , Bola Tinubu, during a ‘thank you visit’ to President Muhammadu Buhari at the State House, Abuja, on Thursday, revealed that he has already  picked a running mate for the 2023 presidential race.
Tinubu visited the President  on Thursday night for a “Thank You” courtesy after winning the APC presidential ticket at the national convention on Wednesday.
